What is Power BI?
Power Bi is a business intelligence tool which you help to analysis the data to clean the data and convert the data into visual formate
where you can create different report and different dashboard so this is the  business intelligence tool

In other language you can say that Power BI is a collection of components
1.	Power Query
Power Query is that the cleaning the data
2.	Power Pivot
Power Pivot is use of the data modeling
3.	Power view
Power view can create 250+ charts
4.	Power BI services
Communicate to the user
